evolving relationship, though they still refused to tell the other
that Logan and Jean were being unfaithful. They didn’t want to be
the cause of heartbreak for each other. They knew Logan and Jean were
busy back at the mansion, alone. Everyone else had business elsewhere
this week, so they were more than happy to keep each other away from
there for a while.</kw></p><p><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3-100">They
