moment she walked into the room that she knew, that she’d known,
and he could’ve slapped himself for being so stupid. Rogue was far
from stupid, and she sure as hell wasn’t blind. </kw><i><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3-90">Of course</kw></i><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3-90">
