and Jean had left again, another motel. It was only more salt to the
wound that it was on his birthday, and they were no doubt getting a
good laugh at his blindness to her infidelity. He didn’t care
though; he’d been meaning to talk to Rogue for a while now. He had
a question, and he was pretty sure her answer would be yes.</kw></p><p><i><kw class="krdwrd-tag-3-70">Scotty
